Subject: cocosys EPP client support Ubuntu 24.04
Description:
Hello,
could you provide me with the epp-client version for Ubuntu 24.04. ?
Thank you
Solution_Comment__c:
Currently we do not have an epp agent for this Ubuntu version.
The EPP client compatible with Ubuntu 24.04 will be available as part of 5.9.4.0 release.(as an estimate July 2024)
